name: Biggs Darklighter (V)
Lore: 'Piloted Red 3 at Battle of Yavin. Childhood friend of Luke. Led mutiny on Rand Ecliptic and theft of Ecliptic from shipyards on Bestine. Ecliptic Evaders emblem on helmet.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys free to Beggar''s Canyon, Red 3, or same location as Fel or Hobbie. While piloting Red 3, it has an [Nav Computer] aboard. During your control phase, may take one Old Times into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
